        <div id="overview" class="doc-card anchor-offset">
          <div class="doc-title">🧭 Overview</div>
          <div class="doc-text">
            The Tenable Vulnerability Management Aging Scans view is an operational hygiene dashboard for scan inventory review.
            It highlights stale scans, ownership gaps, target distribution, recent changes, and scan records that may need review.
            The primary working label in the dashboard is <b>Scan_age</b>, which classifies each scan into one aging bucket.
          </div>
        </div>

